  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. Intended use is limited to static compression-bending loading of non-cannulated pedicle screw spinal constructs per ASTM F1717 at physiologically representative load magnitudes for Class II device 510(k) submission support. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-static-compression-bending",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab1-n6-constructs",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab2-n5-constructs"
  ],
  "hasValidationResult": [
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/nagaraja-compression-bending-vr-001",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "ASTM F1717 static compression-bending FEA vs. experiment comparison — N=11 constructs, two laboratories"
    }
  ],
  "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4043771",
